In [28]:
score_list = []
for k in range(2, 10):
    kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=k)
    kmeans.fit(Xs)
    labels = kmeans.predict(Xs)
    score_list.append(
        {
            "k": k,
            "interia": kmeans.inertia_,
            "bd": davies_bouldin_score(Xs, labels),
            "silhouette": silhouette_score(Xs, labels),
        }
    )
